HEADWORD: Succeeding
<hw>Suc*ceed"ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The act of one who, or that
which, succeeds; also, that which succeeds, or follows after;
consequence.</def> <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

